# Migration Watch — environment variables
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The app itself requires NO environment variables and NO secrets to run or
# build. All tracking data is fetched once at build time from Movebank's PUBLIC
# (no-login) API and bundled into src/data/tracks.json, which is committed.
#
# Copy this file to `.env` only if you intend to re-fetch data from Movebank
# studies that are NOT fully public. These are read by your own fetch commands,
# never by the deployed app, and must never be committed.

# Your Movebank account (only for downloading non-public / login-required studies)
# MOVEBANK_USERNAME=your-username
# MOVEBANK_PASSWORD=your-password
